    <title>Volkmann Names Lori Clark as New VP of Operations</title>
    <link>http://www.powderbulksolids.com/news/Volkmann-Names-Lori-Clark-as-New-VP-of-Operations-01-23-2017</link>
    <description>
          &lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot; property=&quot;dc:date&quot; datatype=&quot;xsd:dateTime&quot; content=&quot;2017-01-23T00:00:00-07:00&quot;&gt;January 23, 2017&lt;/span&gt;    

          &lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.powderbulksolids.com/sites/powderbulksolids.com/files/styles/medium/public/news/images/Lori-Clark-300dpi.jpeg?itok=Bx_GcZT8&quot; width=&quot;220&quot; height=&quot;186&quot; alt=&quot;Lori Clark, the new VP of Operations at Volkmann Inc. Image courtesy of Volkmann&quot; title=&quot;Lori Clark, the new VP of Operations at Volkmann Inc. Image courtesy of Volkmann&quot; /&gt;    

          &lt;p&gt;Designer and manufacturer of product transfer systems, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.volkmannusa.com/&quot;&gt;Volkmann Inc.&lt;/a&gt; named long-time employee Lori Clark as its vice president of operations, the Bristol, PA-based division of Volkmann GmbH announced Jan. 3.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clark, the second employee hired by Volkmann GmbH&amp;rsquo;s American unit, will be responsible for finances, purchasing, and shipping, the company said.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Lori&amp;rsquo;s work ethic and dedication to our success is obvious to all who deal with her,&amp;rdquo; said Nick Hayes, president of Volkmann Inc., in the company&amp;rsquo;s press release. &amp;ldquo;I am confident that she will continue to provide the operational excellence that we are known for throughout our industry to our expanding customer base.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Volkmann said the new leadership position recognizes Clark&amp;rsquo;s contributions to the division and &amp;ldquo;sets the scene&amp;rdquo; for growth moving forward as the company works to provide the market with vacuum conveyors, bag dump stations, bulk bag unloaders, and other powder handling equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.volkmannusa.com/&quot;&gt;VolkmannUSA.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
