          &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://hapman.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Hapman&lt;/a&gt;, a leader in the design and manufacture of equipment and systems for bulk material handling, welcomes Keith Rouse as its new director of marketing of its global operations.&lt;br /&gt;
